2️⃣ Redux Persist:-
.............................

If you are using Redux Toolkit, you can persist the Redux store using Redux Persist.

Library:

Redux Persist

It automatically saves Redux state to AsyncStorage.

Installing Redux Persist
npm install redux-persist
Basic Setup

